## AI Coding Rules (Cursor)

### Stack: {{stack}}

- **Build**: `npm run dev` (Vite), `npm run build` (tsc + vite build)
- **Test**: `npm test` (vitest + jsdom), `npm run test:watch`
- **Structure**: Feature-first under `src/features/`, shared components in `src/shared/`
- **State**: TanStack Query for server data, React context or URL for client state — no Redux
- **Routing**: React Router 7, define routes in a central config
- **Deps**: `react@19`, `react-dom@19`, `react-router@7`, `@tanstack/react-query@5`
- **DevDeps**: `vite`, `@vitejs/plugin-react`, `vitest`, `@testing-library/react`, `jsdom`
- **Tip**: CSS Modules or Tailwind — never inline styles
